claim.claim-text:
11. An apparatus for transferring a file from a portable device to a scanning device, the apparatus comprising:
a display mechanism;
a detection mechanism;
a transferring mechanism configured to transfer, to the scanning device, one or more optical codes that together encode the content of the file, wherein transferring a respective optical code involves:
configuring the display mechanism to display the respective optical code on the display mechanism; and
configuring the detection mechanism to detect that the scanning device successfully scanned the respective optical code.
